'''Agao''' was a [[City/Legends|city]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Bassadro]]. It was located relatively close to the [[Agao Ranges]], a stretch of dormant volcanoes. Sometime during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatists]] claimed that the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]] was responsible for the destruction of [[Agao-Nir]].

